comment:
* Constants for the metadata sync table. This table is used to cache the metadata_sync data
     * from server before it is merged into other CP2 tables.
     *
     * @hide
     * @deprecated These columns were never public since added. They will not be supported
     * as of Android version {@link android.os.Build.VERSION_CODES#R}.

variables.name: METADATA_AUTHORITY
variables.comment: The authority for the contacts metadata

variables.name: METADATA_AUTHORITY_URI
variables.comment: A content:// style uri to the authority for the contacts metadata

variables.name: CONTENT_URI
variables.comment: * The content:// style URI for this table.

variables.name: CONTENT_TYPE
variables.comment: * The MIME type of {@link #CONTENT_URI} providing a directory of contact metadata

variables.name: CONTENT_ITEM_TYPE
variables.comment: * The MIME type of a {@link #CONTENT_URI} subdirectory of a single contact metadata.
